    "final_text": "END USER LICENSE AGREEMENT\n\nLast updated: September 12, 2025\n\nThis End User License Agreement (\"Agreement\") is between you and PrivExpensIA (\"Company\", \"we\", \"us\", or \"our\") regarding your use of PrivExpensIA mobile application (\"App\").\n\n1. LICENSE GRANT\nSubject to your compliance with this Agreement, Company grants you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to download, install, and use the App on your personal devices.\n\n2. RESTRICTIONS\nYou may not: (a) modify, distribute, or create derivative works; (b) reverse engineer or decompile; (c) use for commercial purposes without authorization; (d) violate any applicable laws.\n\n3. PRIVACY\nYour privacy is important. Our Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.\n\n4. SUBSCRIPTIONS\nPremium features require subscription. Subscriptions auto-renew unless cancelled. Refunds subject to App Store policies.\n\n5. DATA OWNERSHIP\nYou retain ownership of your expense data. We provide tools to export your data.\n\n6. TERMINATION\nThis license terminates if you violate terms or delete the App.\n\n7. DISCLAIMERS\nApp provided \"AS IS\" without warranties. Company not liable for financial decisions based on App usage.\n\n8. GOVERNING LAW\nThis Agreement is governed by laws of California, USA.\n\nBy using PrivExpensIA, you agree to these terms."
